cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI

This paper is related to computer security (cs.CR) as it focuses on detecting network attacks. It also involves network infrastructure (cs.NI) as it uses SNMP-MIB interface parameters to detect anomalies. The paper uses machine learning algorithms (cs.AI) and attribute evaluators (cs.LG) to achieve accurate results. Finally, it can be considered as a system and information theory (cs.SI) paper as it proposes an efficient detection model to increase the performance and efficiency of intrusion detection systems.
